<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="making-dockable-dialogs-close-on-esc" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Making Dockable Dialogs Close on Esc</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>All dialogs in Serna close when you press the <uicontrol>Esc</uicontrol> key, except for  the three <xref href="docking.xml">dockable dialogs</xref>: <xref href="inserting-element.xml">Insert Element Dialog</xref>, <xref href="editing-attributes.xml">Element Attributes Dialog</xref> and <xref href="find-replace-with-docked-find-replace-dialog.xml">Find&amp;Replace Dialog</xref>. </p>
      <p>To make these  dockable dialogs close on pressing the <uicontrol>Esc</uicontrol> key, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the <keyword>General tab</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>General tab.</title>
            <image href="preferences-dialog-general-tab-dockable-dialogs.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>On the <uicontrol>Dockable Dialogs</uicontrol> pane, check the <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Close when Escape is pressed</uicontrol>
          </menucascade> checkbox.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Apply</uicontrol> button to apply the settings.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button to close the dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
